rComments: Amazing professor! Loved being a student in his class, very engaging and resourceful lectures. Just do your readings on time, attend class and ask for help whenever you need, he is very helpful! One of the best courses I took during my undergrad.

Honestly one of the most caring and involved teachers at the university. He is always willing to help out students even if it means walking them through the same concept 50 million time. He makes allowances for projects late under certain circumstances. You absolutely must do the readings for this course or you will not pass the final. BEST PROF
